name: seek
description: Seek ahead or behind on a track by seconds or to a specific time.

name: shuffle
description: Toggle shuffling the queue.

name: skip
description: Skip to the next song in the queue.

name: stop
description: Stop playback and clear the queue.

name: volume
description: Set the volume for audio.

name: setlinkquoter enabled
description: Disabling this will make grief stop attempting to quote any message link that is sent in this server.

name: setlinkquoter crossserver
description: Disabling this will make grief stop attempting to quote any message link that is sent in other servers shared by grief.

name: setlinkquoter deletemessage
description: Disabling this will make grief stop attempting to delete any message link that is sent by grief.

name: setlinkquoter webhooks
description: Enabling this will make grief stop attempting to send any message link by webhook.

name: setlinkquoter showsettings
description: Shows the current linkquoter settings.

name: setlinkquoter whitelist
description: Whitelist/unwhitelist a channel from being affected by linkquoter.

name: nitrorole addmessage
description: Add new booster message. Leave blank for variables.

name: nitrorole autoassignrole
description: Set a role that will be autoassigned after someone boosts server.

name: nitrorole channel
description: Set channel for new booster messages. Leave empty to disable.

name: nitrorole listmessages
description: List booster message templates.

name: nitrorole removemessage
description: Remove new booster message.

name: nitrorole unassignonboostend
description: Set if booster role should be unassigned when someone stops boosting server.

name: suggestset anonymous
description: Toggle whether server suggestions are anonymous.

name: suggestset approved
description: Set the channel for approved suggestions.

name: suggestset autodelete
description: Toggle whether after the suggest command, the bot deletes the command message.

name: suggestset channel
description: Set the channel for suggestions.

name: suggestset delete
description: Toggle whether suggestions in the original suggestion channel get deleted after being approved/rejected.

name: suggestset rejected
description: Set the channel for rejected suggestions.

name: suggestset same
description: Set whether to use the same channel for new and finished suggestions.

name: suggestset settings
description: See the settings for suggestions.

name: suggest
description: Submit a suggestion.

name: approve
description: Approve a suggestion.

name: reject
description: Reject a suggestion.

name: addreason
description: Add a reason to a rejected suggestion.

name: showsuggestion
description: Show a suggestion.
